{"tid":212384,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[賭波台] 馬會開香港波賭波合法化有冇得諗？","createTime":"2017-04-22T11:31:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-22T18:37:29.000Z","uid":59491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fa7f8d9be974a56d68ff5f6c09a3267c1a28e008","tid":212384,"uid":59491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T11:31:33.000Z","msg":"資料 A<br />\n<br />\n剛誕生的新加坡聯賽百廢待興，加上地下賭波集團干擾，早年的賽事「黑哨」橫行，球賽勝負也難分真與假。但李氏畢竟是強政勵治的政治家，亦敢於為天下先。新加坡政府率先將本地足球博彩合化法，除了成功打擊賭波集團外，又將博彩稅款用來發展青訓、場地等足球事業，另一邊廂又嚴禁球員收受利益。據說，新加坡聯賽從此站穩陣腳，各球隊得益於博彩收益亦達至收支平衡，其班霸「新加坡武裝部隊」（後改稱勇士足球會），更在2010年殺入亞冠盃分組賽，以一個新成立的聯賽而言，已屬難能可貴。<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/sports/player?newsId=sp12144952629\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Fsports%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3Dsp12144952629&d=u6RaX9rkx0MxONw5VJESxQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=8a778b02\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Fsports%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3Dsp12144952629&h=a43554b8\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/sports/player?newsId=sp12144952629</a><br />\n<br />\n資料 B<br />\n<br />\n浸會大學體育學系副教授雷雄德認為，本地波博彩現在「未係時候」。他指出，英國可以合法賭當地波，全因當地有一套成熟的系統監察打假波。「如果明知班友打假波，點會有人買？如果制度未健全，就推行本地波博彩，再搞多幾單假波出來，成個足運就會散晒。」<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20140113/18590091\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20140113%2F18590091&d=u6RaX9rkx0MxONw5VJESxQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=1e7f2622\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20140113%2F18590091&h=5fe14c58\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20140113/18590091</a><br />\n<br />\n資料 C<br />\n伍健:<br />\n在討論應否賭本地波的問題前，首先要作兩個假設，否則很難有共識地討論下去。第一，我們要先拋開賭錢是否應該的道德問題，每個人的價值觀不同，即使傾多幾年，都不可能有共識。第二，要監管因賭本地波而可能引發的行賄問題，是需要一個全面的監察程度，才可以有效的做到。只靠球員個人的操守，效果不彰之餘，亦不易消除公眾的疑慮。（我不是不相信球員的道德水準，相反我很相信他們的操守。但要公眾相信，卻又是另一件事。）  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/notes/ken-k-ng/%E8%B3%AD%E6%B3%A2%E6%95%91%E6%B8%AF%E7%94%B2/264086083614725/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fnotes%2Fken-k-ng%2F%25E8%25B3%25AD%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E6%2595%2591%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%2594%25B2%2F264086083614725%2F&d=u6RaX9rkx0MxONw5VJESxQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=084b83d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/notes/ken-k-ng/%E8%B3%AD%E6%B3%A2%E6%95%91%E6%B8%AF%E7%94%B2/264086083614725/</a>"},{"pid":"efff9635c12055434a27c6f290e9c53e2520fcdc","tid":212384,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T11:33:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5bfba97c9a51896fa128fc5802208d03cfe84c65","tid":212384,"uid":14719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T13:05:23.000Z","msg":"信得過icac咪得"},{"pid":"68384206c97141c4cc75b87ebee3f1044867aa29","tid":212384,"uid":59491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T18:37:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}